vyges-layout is a memory-safe Rust layout-geometry kernel: GDSII read/write,
polygon boolean operations, and hierarchy flattening. It is the substrate under
layout-side tooling (LVS device extraction, DRC, metal fill) and the chip viewer.

This is a clean-room implementation; no third-party EDA database is included.
